title: I AM ATHLETE (S2E1) | The NBA Bubble & NFL Restart
description:
On the season 2 premiere of I AM ATHLETE, we welcome Chad Johnson to the crew and discuss life in the NBA bubble, the NFL upcoming season and shooting of Jacob Blake.

I Am Athlete podcast is candid, unscripted weekly discussion between former NFL greats: Brandon Marshall, Chad Johnson, Fred Taylor and Channing Crowder. 

A new episode premieres every Monday at 12pm Eastern.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Alicia Zubikowski)
